      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly in pristine condition\u2014looks and drives just like it did the day it left the lot. I've absolutely babied this car, and it really shows in every detail. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
