    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it still carries that new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive service history with every oil change and inspection performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with factory precision, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance records. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence in its purest form.",
      "price": 48900.0,
