      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe your eyes when you see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely flawless condition and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, totally sparkling. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I'm so excited about it!",
